   "body" : "Libraries may not be upgraded in time to handle the new serialization when segwit blocks and transactions come into the mainchain. This flag would allow people to use the RPC interface uninterrupted and intentionally upgrade as needed.\r\n\r\nIt's affecting users [today](https://www.reddit.com/r/Bitcoin/comments/5dx86y/psa_segwit_changes_the_format_of_data_returned_by/). \r\n\r\nupdate: I have added a command line flag instead. See below.",
